Installation and config of venv and flask

1. create folder
2. open folder in vsc
3. open terminal and run "python -m venv virtual"
4. to activate venv "cd virtual\Scripts" and type "activate"
5. back to project root "cd ../.."
8. Install flask in venv "pip install Flask"
9. To deactivate "cd virtual\Scripts" and type "deactivate"

Developing web using flask

1. create file
2. make sure in the terminal app.py is
3. run "flask run" and it will start server at port 5000
4. open web and type the address (localhost:5000)